OL,3,CNew cafe, bar and restaurant unveiled
OL,4,Cin Jersey Airport revamp
OL,6,FA UK company has been chosen to run
OL,7,FJersey Airport's new eatery, named The
OL,8,FShoreline Cafe Bar & Kitchen.
OL,10,FPorts of Jersey says the long-term
OL,11,Fpartnership with The Restaurant Group
OL,12,FConcessions (TRGC) will expand its
OL,13,Ffood and drink options, offering "a
OL,14,Ffaster, more flexible service for
OL,15,Fpassengers".
OL,17,FThe restaurant is set to open past
OL,18,Fsecurity in early 2027, as part of a
OL,19,Fwider revamp of the departures hall.
