OL,3,CNew cafe, bar and restaurant unveiled
OL,4,Cin Jersey Airport revamp
OL,6,FTRGC has more than three decades of
OL,7,Fexperience in travel hospitality,
OL,8,Foperating dining options in airports
OL,9,Fworldwide.
OL,11,FThe existing deal with local firm
OL,12,FJersey Pottery Restaurants (JPR) will
OL,13,Fbe wound down - although Cafe Ube will
OL,14,Fremain open until the new eatery is in
OL,15,Fplace.
OL,17,FExisting JPR staff will move over to
OL,18,FTRGC as part of the transition, Ports
OL,19,Fadds.
