OL,3,CNew cafe, bar and restaurant unveiled
OL,4,Cin Jersey Airport revamp
OL,6,FThe new restaurant will have 228 seats
OL,7,Fand serve hot meals, plus lighter
OL,8,Fbites, grab-and-go options, coffee and
OL,9,Falcoholic drinks.
OL,11,FPorts says the brand has been inspired
OL,12,Fby the island's landscape and identity
OL,13,Fand will have a commitment to
OL,14,Fsupplying local produce.
OL,16,FMatt Thomas, Ports of Jersey Chief
OL,17,FExecutive Officer, adds: "Today
OL,18,Fsignals an exciting long-term
OL,19,Finvestment in Jersey Airport's future.
